{"tid":881325,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"比起一次性優惠，港鐵應用更多資源防止同類大規模事故","createTime":"2018-10-29T11:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T13:00:56.000Z","uid":30647,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1bf16013a17465d4694a24d7d53844bb9c41f1bb","tid":881325,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T11:04:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181029/large/1540805815_3c29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181029%2Flarge%2F1540805815_3c29.jpg&h=dd2d17bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大學生林小姐稱，比起一次性優惠，港鐵應用更多資源防止同類大規模事故，亦應停止加價<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n享用學生優惠的大學生林小姐表示，冧檔當日遇上考試，比原定到校時間遲了半小時，在開考前5分鐘趕到，「最後（考試）係cancel咗，太多同學返唔到嚟」。她也稱，比起一次性優惠，港鐵應用更多資源防止同類大規模事故，亦應停止加價，「不過都無乜可能（不加價），因為佢哋要賺錢」。今次優惠在周六和周日推出，她表示自己住在土瓜灣，除了上學一般也不會乘搭港鐵，故今次優惠無法享用，「唔會刻意去搭，同埋出街都只係去一、兩個地方」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181029/58849794\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181029%2F58849794&d=MzqCjGERpgcm%2BCiWhigIojANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=33ad13e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181029%2F58849794&h=2ec87900\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181029/58849794</a>"},{"pid":"5b5377c94c7a6b45578a976d8df8c5e8a62ca325","tid":881325,"uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T11:06:23.000Z","msg":"林小姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8da16a730cee08bba507d957aaa1000e239db378","tid":881325,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T11:55:50.000Z","msg":"的確<br />\n所以個方法就係俾少d資源高層，俾少d利潤公司，去鞭策佢地、懲罰佢地，而慳返嚟錢就攞去換設備。"},{"pid":"5343c8ad121b8fea23645a4d12ca9127c9bffafe","tid":881325,"uid":79170,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T11:56:46.000Z","msg":"林小姐一次性優惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356d3e2ad503b572b8813451746617c2ed756233","tid":881325,"uid":192190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T11:58:34.000Z","msg":"起一次, 性優惠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20fe0b81bdd9d8ef873b9076867b5676b48901d2","tid":881325,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T12:26:27.000Z","msg":"如果大型事故會可以令港鐵唔加價<br />\n咁港鐵肯定以後唔駛加價"},{"pid":"5097e1ebee7105ae71d1e17ea073f1db98e5aa1d","tid":881325,"uid":216396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20fe0b81bdd9d8ef873b9076867b5676b48901d2","tid":881325,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T12:26:27.000Z","msg":"如果大型事故會可以令港鐵唔加價<br />\n咁港鐵肯定以後唔駛加價"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T12:33:17.000Z","msg":"如果有撚用咩，地鐵公司同政府都唔撚做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9b9b67d76e4556228499d58db6a76442938777","tid":881325,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5097e1ebee7105ae71d1e17ea073f1db98e5aa1d","tid":881325,"uid":216396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20fe0b81bdd9d8ef873b9076867b5676b48901d2","tid":881325,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T12:26:27.000Z","msg":"如果大型事故會可以令港鐵唔加價<br />\n咁港鐵肯定以後唔駛加價"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T12:33:17.000Z","msg":"如果有撚用咩，地鐵公司同政府都唔撚做嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji